
===================================================================

This example shows how to run 

-------------------------------------------------------------------

cp.x to do String method (SMD) to find the
minimum energy path (MEP) of

H + H2 -> H2 + H

To used this method, one must know the initial
and the final states. They should be obtained
using regular CP optimization before running the SMD.


!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

This example is for an illustration purpose only.
It does not represent any physical descriptions because
the accuracy is considerablly reduced for fast convegence. 

The attached "intro.pdf" may be helpful for practical usages.

------------------------------------------------------------------

This script runs a sequence of 7 optimization steps to find the MEP,
using 2nd order damped dynamics.

It first optimizes the electronic degrees of 
freedom for the string (step 1-4), 
then it starts SMD optimization to find the MEP (step 5-7), 
sequentially.

To run the script from x-th step to y-th step, execute

./run_example x y 

e.g.

./run_example 5 7 

executes the steps 5, 6 and 7.

--------------------------------------------------------------


